  "summary": [
    "Fix the stale partial-approval migration regression so valid newer additive Alembic heads do not fail the complete suite",
    "Split CRM dispatch into downward compliance requests and upward compliance submissions",
    "Allow fresh and pending complaints to be assigned to lower offices before an official reply exists",
    "Require finalized official-letter complete packets for submission to the CEO or another higher office",
    "Add complaint-level report, reply, policy and evidence uploads linked to dispatch requests",
    "Include accepted lower-office files in later complete official-letter PDFs",
    "Add office-level and allowed-direction controls to reusable WhatsApp destination profiles",
    "Add deterministic direction-aware routing and manual override safeguards",
    "Repair routing modal opacity, scrolling and visible save actions",
    "Add Select All, workflow-specific purposes and direction-aware dispatch history",
    "Preserve immutable WhatsApp preview, approval, idempotency, queueing and delivery audit infrastructure",
    "Run complete project tests and Astro build by default with transactional rollback"
  ],
